<HEADLINE> Snowboarding World Cup Cancelled </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
VIENNA, December 5 (Xinhua) -- A heavy storm caused organizers
to cancel Saturday's giant slalom at the Snowboarding World Cup
race in Ischgl, Austria, reports said reaching here.
</P>
<P>
The fourth World Cup event of the season will resume on Sunday
with the snowboarding cross if the weather is fine enough.
</P>
