<HEADLINE> Opening Ceremony of Asian Games Starts in Bangkok </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 6 (Xinhua) -- The opening ceremony for the
13th Asian Games was started here at 18:30 local time Sunday
evening.
</P>
<P>
And Thai king Bhumibol Adulyadej is to officially declare the
opening of the Games at around eight o'clock in the evening.
</P>
<P>
This was the fourth time that Thailand plays hosts to the
quadrennial regional sports gala.
</P>
<P>
The Asian Games held its inaugural meet in New Dehli in 1951,
and Thailand had hosted the meet three times in 1966, 1970 and
1978. 
